Subject: clk: tegra: Add support for OSC_DIV fixed clocks

Git-commit: 9a85eb4d62425555ccdc774d906e6bbca5ffccc0
Patch-mainline: v5.7-rc1
References: jsc#SLE-15847

Tegra30 through Tegra210 has OSC_DIV2 and OSC_DIV4 fixed clocks
from the OSC pads.

This patch adds support for these clocks.

Tested-by: Dmitry Osipenko <digetx@gmail.com>
